---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro'
---
<Base
  title="research synthesis — janice quach"
  description="turn your raw research into structured decisions. themes, insights, tensions, priority actions — delivered within 48 hours. $300 per engagement."
>
  <a href="/" class="back-btn">← home</a>

  <section class="synthesis">
    <div class="orb orb-1" aria-hidden="true"></div>
    <div class="orb orb-2" aria-hidden="true"></div>

    <div class="content">
      <p class="eyebrow">research synthesis</p>
      <h1>raw transcripts.<br><em>structured decisions.</em></h1>
      <p class="lede">you did the research. i'll turn it into something your team can act on.</p>
      <p class="price">$300 · delivered within 48 hours</p>

      <div class="rule" aria-hidden="true"></div>

      <p class="body">paste your transcripts, notes, or survey exports — raw is fine. you'll get back a structured report: key themes with direct evidence, insights mapped to concrete design implications, the tensions your data raises (not smoothed over), and priority actions ranked by impact.</p>
      <p class="body">no revision cycles. scope is defined by what you submit. the more signal, the stronger the synthesis.</p>

      <a href="https://synthesis.janicequach.workers.dev" class="cta">submit your research →</a>
    </div>
  </section>
</Base>

<style>
  .synthesis {
    position: relative;
    min-height: 100vh;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    overflow: hidden;
    padding: 6rem 2rem;
  }

  .orb-1 {
    position: absolute;
    width: 500px;
    height: 500px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    pointer-events: none;
    background: radial-gradient(circle at 40% 40%, rgba(213, 196, 220, 0.35), transparent 70%);
    top: -100px;
    right: -80px;
  }

  .orb-2 {
    position: absolute;
    width: 350px;
    height: 350px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    pointer-events: none;
    background: radial-gradient(circle at 60% 60%, rgba(200, 213, 192, 0.3), transparent 70%);
    bottom: -60px;
    left: -60px;
  }

  .content {
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
    max-width: 600px;
    width: 100%;
  }

  .eyebrow {
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    font-weight: 500;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.15em;
    color: rgba(42, 37, 32, 0.5);
    margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
  }

  h1 {
    font-size: clamp(2.5rem, 6vw, 4rem);
    line-height: 1.1;
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
    color: #2a2520;
    margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
  }

  h1 em {
    font-style: italic;
  }

  .lede {
    font-size: 1.0625rem;
    color: rgba(42, 37, 32, 0.6);
    line-height: 1.7;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  .price {
    font-size: 0.9375rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: #2a2520;
    margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
  }

  .rule {
    width: 48px;
    height: 1px;
    background: rgba(42, 37, 32, 0.2);
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }

  .body {
    font-size: 1rem;
    color: rgba(42, 37, 32, 0.65);
    line-height: 1.8;
    margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
  }

  .cta {
    display: inline-block;
    margin-top: 2rem;
    font-size: 0.9375rem;
    font-weight: 500;
    letter-spacing: 0.02em;
    color: #f4f1eb;
    background: #2a2520;
    padding: 1rem 2.5rem;
    border-radius: 8px;
    text-decoration: none;
    transition: background 0.2s ease, transform 0.2s cubic-bezier(0.16, 1, 0.3, 1);
  }

  .cta:hover {
    background: #45403a;
    transform: translateY(-2px);
  }

  .cta:active {
    transform: translateY(0);
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .synthesis {
      align-items: flex-start;
      padding: 5rem 1.5rem 4rem;
    }

    h1 {
      font-size: 2.5rem;
    }
  }
</style>
